{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/xcwkez/","result":{"data":{"sitePage":null},"pageContext":{"url":"posts/xcwkez","relativePath":"posts/xcwkez","frontmatter":{"title":"在视频会议中高效传递知识","stackbit_url_path":"posts/xcwkez","date":"2022-07-12T03:41:27","excerpt":"","tags":[],"categories":[],"template":"post"},"html":"<p>疫情让远程办公成为新常态，面对面沟通变少，而视频会议大大增多。当涉及到一些知识分享时，大家往往习惯于让分享者共享电脑屏幕并讲解，但是实际发现效果并不好。主讲者往往要再三确认，能听见吗？能看见吗？有问题吗？尤其是有问题吗这个问题，往往由于大家是静音状态，导致冷场。关键是，往往听者处于分心状态，或者只是挂个机而已。</p>\n<p>这时不妨反过来，让听者来分享屏幕，而主讲人则给予指导，听者在指示下操作屏幕，主讲人根据操作给予语音反馈。这样似乎对听者有点不太礼貌，但是效果却更好，听者完全主动参与了知识分享的过程，操作上有任何疑问就实时提问，从而最后是自己去发现、探索从而索取到了需要的知识。</p>\n<p>这种方法在一对一的视频会议中尤其有效，如果从多的话，可能需要轮流操作，或者使用第三方白板工具来辅助一下了。</p>","pages":[],"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jeff Tian","author":"@zizhujy","description":"A wild full stack developer","palette":"yellow","header":{"title":"Jeff Tian","tagline":"A wild developer","logo_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7z1ua3nTOC5B7DwwzAki8I/4e1a05f8db770c285a492eeb1eaa398f/imageedit_3_2509022194.png","background_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7m0jrKYaDBwEvlc5lo8nt6/6d50a5050d9cdc0d4d2047e35feac292/10648733_696750647079056_2800539603462658695_o.jpg","has_nav":true,"nav_links":[{"label":"Home","url":"/","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"About","url":"/about","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"关于","url":"https://ggyy.pa-pa.me/about","style":"link","icon_class":"lorem-ipsum","new_window":true,"type":"action"},{"label":"Contact","url":"/contact","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"Support Me","url":"/support-me","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"叽叽歪歪","url":"https://ggyy.pa-pa.me/","style":"link","icon_class":"lorem-ipsum","new_window":true,"type":"action"}],"has_social":true,"social_links":[{"label":"Twitter","url":"https://twitter.com/zizhujy","style":"icon","icon_class":"fa-twitter","new_window":true,"type":"action"},{"label":"Instagram","url":"https://www.instagram.com/jefftian5","style